I'm still alive.

Don't worry.

Lets see..things that have happened since Daria dumped Jared.

-I think I'm still obsessed with Jared.
-There was a dance last Friday
-I slowdanced with Craig twice
-Everyone wanted Craig to ask me out.
-I slept over Megan's after the dance, went around Smithfield, Lincoln, and Attleboro, with her most of Saturday, then went to her half-sister, Hanah's, second birthday party. (Which was fun.)
-Craig barely talked to me this week.
-Amanda said she was going out with Derek. But then I find out Derek is going out with Krystal. (WTF?)
-Megan wants to dump Paul (ssshhh!!)
-Paul supposedly is 'obsessed' with Megan. (Or so she heard.)
-Ashley and her friends started to fight again. She sat with us at lunch. Was lots of fun.
-I want to change the name of my website to 'Animated Reality' (Take that idea and die bitches.)
-I got a 45/50 on one of my Math Quizzes, a 105 on my History Quiz, andddd a 4/4 on my ending paragraph to 'The Tell Tale Heart' 
- Today I bought things for my Shoe-box project for English, I worked on the CoverPage for Sarah's biography also for English, and I think I finished my Salem Witch Trial drawing. I just need to write like a 750 word thing to go with it or something like that. I also bought 'Shopoholic Takes Manhatten' since I finished my other Shopaholic book. =)

Yeah I think that's it.

which is totally stupid but i found jeans that fit me because im inbetween a size 12 and 14..xD so i can barely ever find anything that fits x_X

..so anyway..yeah in Rave Girl..there was this lady that talked to us for about an hour..got she scares people out of the store because she talks to much. she was telling my mother how my mom looks like a movie star and crap. and how she had 7 kids..and got re-married and shit.. ask yourself this before you speak "do you really think that a married woman with two kids that are school shopping and just want to get it over with ACTUALLY want to talk about this crap?" 

..hah i can answer that!

no.

So yeah. then at Rave Girl..they didn't take checks so my mom flipped out and started getting all angry and shit at me and Jackie, so she put the clothes on hold. And then as we were going down the elevator..to the second floor..when we thought we were going to the first to go back into the car..as we got off the elevator jackie stepped on my flip-flop and it felt like i stepped on glass. matter of fact it still feels like it now. then we went into sears..the clothes..just suck. i tried on a pair of jeans..that looked okay but i didn't buy them. Then we went into Limited Too, then  we went to Aeropostale..i liked a few shirts..but then Jackie expired and my mom didn't want to pay for lunch so we just left. 

My mom said she'll take me shopping when Jackie goes to school on the first. 

-thank god-

well the sleepover was fun. okay so like it was liv, me, sarah k., nicole m, nicole p., calli, alicia, kelsey, erin and ryan.

it took me and my dad a while to find the street..because her street doesn't have a sign..so we were going up man school road like all that way past conor's farm and stuff and then i had to call liv and ask her which street was hers xD

but yeah when i got there we just sat in the living room and just talked..i talked to kelsey the most. liv's house is very nice though. xD she's an only child so it's all like neat and clean and stuff. which is cool. amanda never showed up because she had a 'family thing' or so she texted me on my dad's phone. which was okay. when me and nicole and kelsey were talking about hot topic...i told her about the Gir plushie i wanted there and she's like to liv "she wants the gar plushie at hot topic" and i go "no i want gir 'g-i-rrr!'" when i meant to say -r- but instead i said -errr- and kelsey started laughing so hard xD

then we watched chicago..which was a really cool movie i mean they dance so freaking good. i wanna dance like that lol. kelsey tried to sleep towards the end but calli and alicia were wayyy to loud to try and sleep lol. and when the movie ended me and sarah played the musical scenes and danced to it while everyone was in the kitchen, well except for erin, sarah, me and kelsey. and they were teaching me how to do a bridge. on like pillows and like between their hands lol heh...it sorta worked i guess xD then yeah..everyone made smores and we ate those xD which were kinda messy but i got the first one lmao. just because im special like that. we opened presents before chicago..i forgot to mention that but thats okay. xD she gots lotsa cool gifts xD i just got her a gift card and i made her a blend of evanescence, yellocard, and new found glory. everyone liked it. so do i. xD okay then we went into the study and looked up what people's names meant. which was cool. then we went back in the living room and kept watching the jail block tango scene in chicago lol. and then we just talked. about boys...people..all that great stuff. alicia, sarah, nicole p., and calli all have boyfriends.. i was like =( and sarah said she couldn't believe that i dont have a boyfriend. alicia, erin, and sarah all said i was pretty.. heh only if i thought that sometime. but whatever. single-ness is oka-no-it sucks. yeah. oh well.

then calli and alicia wouldn't shut up when we were all trying to sleep...and everyone was getting pissed at them..so sarah and kelsey went to sleep in the study and i joined them like 5 minutes later because i couldn't take it anymore. but thats okay. i finallly got to sleep xD

then like this morning erin, nicole m., and me were up..then we woke up liv and the other nicole and we ate donuts. xD which were good. then eveyone else got up...got dressed..talked and yeah. we had to drag kelsey out of bed..well olivia did anyway..she dragged her right through the kitchen lol! it was so funny.

..then daddy picked me up at like 10:50.. which is TOO early! i mean no fair! well ryan did leave with her mom before me anyway but thats okay xD

but yeah it was fun lol.
